com.edatasource.receipts.helper

Class Validate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.edatasource.receipts.helper.Validate

  • public class Validate
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class which is used to assert that the parsed data is valid.

    It is recommended that parser developers use this class to validate that the data being parsed is what they expect to be returned. This class will automatically cause specific rules and error notifications to be triggered in the parsing framework.
